<div class="centered">
  <% if !flash[:notice].blank? %>
    <div class="alert alert-info">
      <%= flash[:notice] %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <h1 class="main-header">Welcome to the INCS Online Resume Bank</h1>

  <% if session[:user_id] != nil && User.find(session[:user_id]).access == 'pending' %>
    <p>Thank you for your registration. Please allow up to 2 business days for INCS staff to process approval of your account. You have received an email with further information.</p>
  <% end %>

  <% if session[:user_id] == nil %>
    <div class="main-container">
      <%= button_to "Candidate Resume Bank and Job Fair Registration", users_new_teacher_path, method: :get, class: "btn btn-info main-btn"%>
      <%= button_to "School Leader Resume Bank Registration", users_new_school_path, method: :get, class: "btn btn-info main-btn"%>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <% if session[:user_id] != nil && User.find(session[:user_id]).access == 'teacher' && User.find(session[:user_id]).register2017 == 'bank' %>
    <div class="main-container">
    <%= button_to "Register for Job Fair", users_register_path, method: :post, class: "btn btn-info main-btn" %>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <h2 class="topic">
    <br>
    2017 INCS Teacher Job Fair
  </h2>

  <p class="main-content">
  The Illinois Network of Charter Schools (INCS) will host our 12th annual Teacher Job Fair on Saturday, March 18, 2017 at ASPIRA Business & Finance Campus. Representatives from the state’s charter schools will be on hand to recruit hundreds of teachers, social workers, counselors, nurses, and other administrators. INCS seeks highly qualified candidates who are excited to work in a mission-drive environment and to TEACH, LEAD, and SUCCEED. To upload your resume into our <span style="text-decoration: underline">year-round database</span>, please select “Candidate Resume Bank Registration” above.
  </p>



  <p class="main-content">
  <strong>Candidates have the opportunity to:</strong>
  <ul class="main-content-list">
    <li>Meet recruiters from over 50 public charter schools representing over 120 campuses</li>
    <li>Post your resume in the INCS Online Resume Bank, where charter schools look for candidates for various positions year-round</li>
    <li>Interview on-site with schools looking to hire great teachers and administrators like you</li>
    <li><span class="red">NEW THIS YEAR! </span>We will be raffling off one iPad and five $100 gift cards! Instructions for the raffle will be given at the registration desk.</li>
  </ul>
  </p>

  <p class="main-content">
  <strong>Schools have the opportunity to:</strong>
  <ul class="main-content-list">
    <li>Meet with hundreds of educators</li>
    <li>View candidates’ resumes and credentials ahead of time using the INCS Online Resume Bank</li>
    <li>Invite candidates for on-site interviews following the meet and greet portion of the event</li>
  </ul>
  </p>

  <p class="main-content"><strong>Agenda</strong></p>
  <p class="main-content">
  <ul class="main-content-list">
    <li>9:00 am - 10:00 am: School table set-up and Candidate Registration</li>
    <li>10:00 am - 12:00 pm: Meet and greet with Candidates & Schools</li>
    <li>12:00 pm - 1:30 pm: On-site teacher interviews (by invitation only)</li>
  </ul>
  </p>

  <%# <p class="main-content"><strong>Registration</strong></p> %>
  <%# <p class="main-content"> %>
  <%# Candidate check-in will open at 8:30am. <span style="text-decoration: underline">On-site registration is available</span>. Advance registration is encouraged to avoid extended wait times. %>
  <%# </p> %>

  <p class="main-content"><strong>Location</strong></p>
  <p class="main-content">
  ASPIRA Business & Finance Campus, 2989 N. Milwaukee Ave, Chicago, IL 60618
  </p>

  <% if session[:user_id] == nil %>
    <div class="main-container">
      <%= button_to "Candidate Job Fair Registration", users_new_teacher_path, method: :get, class: "btn btn-info main-btn" %>
      <%= button_to "School Leader Job Fair Registration", "https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd2POlBM9yr-WfNbRYFOhnTAZCNg8mfF8gFhfSNKCEm2RACsw/viewform?c=0&w=1", method: :get, class: "btn btn-info main-btn" %>
    </div><br>
  <% end %>

  <p class="main-content underline">
    PARKING
  </p>
  <p class="main-content">
  Parking is limited and public transportation is encouraged. Street parking is available on Milwaukee and a few side streets surrounding ASPIRA’s campus. Please be aware of permitted parking zones. Candidates are <span class="underline">NOT</span> permitted to park in the ASPIRA parking lot.
  </p>
  <p class="main-content underline">
    CANDIDATE ENTRANCE
  </p>
  <p class="main-content">
    Please enter the school through the entrance on Monticello. Please do not enter through Milwaukee. 
  </p>
  <p class="main-content underline">
    PUBLIC TRANSPORTATION DIRECTIONS
  </p>
  <p class="main-content underline">
    CTA BLUE Line
  </p>
  <p class="main-content">
    <span class="underline">Belmont Stop:</span> The school is approximately 0.5 mile southwest of the Belmont Blue Line stop, about a 10 minute walk.
  </p>
  <p class="main-content underline">
    Bus Transportation
  </p>
  <p class="main-content">
    #56 Milwaukee: Take #56 to Milwaukee & Ridgeway. This stop is a 1-minute walk to the ASPIRA Business & Finance campus.
  </p>

